This Folder contains the dataset collected for the month of January, February, March, and April 2020 on the Topic of COVID-19 
in the Geographical area of the United states and Canada. 

The Data contains information about each tweet issued on this topic and detailed information on the person behind the tweet. 

The data is divided into two parts due to equipment constrains 

part 1: contins the tweets for the four months. 
part 2: contains the underlying network for the cleaned data, which is further minimized to agents who update their opinions 30% of the discussion
duration. 
